data.description: OPEN HOUSE 11/11 11AM - 1PM! This stunning residence boasts finishes of pure luxury and thoughtful design. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a formal dining room, perfect for hosting elegant gatherings and creating lasting memories. The living room is a cozy haven, featuring a gas fireplace setting the mood for relaxation. Slide open the doors to the wooden deck. The kitchen, adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances, a convenient breakfast bar, and a pantry that provides ample storage space. Equipped with a main floor laundry room. Retreat to the master bedroom suite and revel in the luxury of a large walk-in closet and double vanities in the ensuite bathroom. The finished walk-out basement offers versatility and potential featuring a large family room, storage area and an additional bedroom and bath. The oversized 3-car garage provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. A home where every detail has truly been carefully curated for your comfort and enjoyment.
